name: #006 - NO CHAIR
description: It’s time to meet a new character, right? This is Cathy! I know se looks like a human, but trust me, she isn’t. Remember her name, she’ll have an important role in Elon’s life. Sorry? What do you mean by “there’s something missing there”? OH MY GOD! She was supposed to be sitting on a chair, right? BUT THERE IS NO CHAIR THERE! OK, I really apologize for that. Feel free to take this one with 50% OFF, it was my mistake! Made on beeplegenerator.com and packaged with love and affection.
